<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="pessimistic-adj">pessimistic <strong><em>adj</em></strong></h1>
<p>英 /ˌpesɪ'mɪstɪk/    美 /ˌpesɪ'mɪstɪk/  </p>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1">1.★ <strong>悲观的；悲观主义的</strong></h4>
<p>反 optimistic： </p>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>The doctors are <strong>pessimistic about</strong> his chances of recovery. 
医生们对他康复的可能性很不乐观。</p></div></div>